importance of book availability.

00:23:51.860 --> 00:23:54.240
And I know this is something
that you care deeply about.

00:23:54.240 --> 00:23:57.860
So if you could speak just a
little bit to book availability

00:23:57.860 --> 00:24:00.210
and how that impacts
reading across the lifespan.

