&gt;&gt; Dustin Holland: Yeah, sure.

00:24:01.510 --> 00:24:02.810
Thanks, Josh.

00:24:02.810 --> 00:24:05.050
And first, I'd like to
thank everybody in the room

00:24:05.050 --> 00:24:07.940
for what you're doing to
promote lifelong learning

00:24:07.940 --> 00:24:11.570
and especially creating
