collect over a billion books

00:24:27.730 --> 00:24:30.230
and keep a billion
books out of landfills

00:24:30.230 --> 00:24:32.270
and keep them in
the reuse cycle.

00:24:32.270 --> 00:24:37.960
So to date, we've kept over 300
million books out of landfills

00:24:37.960 --> 00:24:40.640
in about six countries.

00:24:40.640 --> 00:24:44.730
We've sold over 75 million
books and shipped those books

00:24:44.730 --> 00:24:47.580
to customers in over
